title: Nidal gave his crush the ULTIMATE GIFT
author: Juju & Nidal
description:
In the ultimate surprise, we flew back out to California to surprise Salish for her birthday! The two of them thought they'd never see each other again...watch them reunite after a long time away!

As always, everyone, thank you so much for watching!! If you enjoyed it, let us know in the comments below or with a like and subscribe!
